MidPoint 4.9 "Verne" Update 7
-------------------------------

Release 4.9.7 is a seventy-eighth midPoint release code-named Verne.
The 4.9.7 release brings security, stability and miscellaneous bugfixes.

Release date: 1st June 2026
Release type: Maintenance release
End of support: 18th October 2026

Please see the release notes for detailed list of changes:
https://docs.evolveum.com/midpoint/release/4.9.7/
